  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is filed under the Minimal profile; the signature workflow is pending and no digital signature is present. Hash is recorded for future countersignature. Full 13-factor assessment carried forward from the Morrison COU2 base case.",
